@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_apepik(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((v1 - wp.exp(v2 + 0.74)) * v1)
    v1 = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.56) + wp.abs(v1 + 0.30)) - (wp.exp(v2 + 0.88) / (v0 + 0.58 - v2 + 0.51)))
    tmp = wp.exp(0.30)
    v1 = (v1 - wp.cos(wp.cos(v1 + 0.61)))
    v2 = wp.exp((0.68 / (v2 + 1.00 * v1 + 0.44)))
    v0 = 0.33
    v2 = tmp
    v2 = 0.81
    data[tid] = v0
